data.description: This beautiful open concept condo offers first floor living at it's best. Upon entering you will find the living room w/ vaulted ceilings, dining room, pantry & storage closets. The kitchen w/ breakfast bar features oak cabinets, updated solid surface countertops & glass mosaic backsplash. The attached 2 car garage is just off the kitchen, making unloading grocery's a breeze.  2 generously sized bedrooms, each w/ their own private bath & walk in closet. Enjoy a book or cup of coffee on the covered front porch while taking in the peace and quiet of the natural surroundings. Many updates include appliances, air conditioner, flooring throughout, windows & walk in shower w/ glass door. This great property is close to the library, shopping, dining, and groce
